#
# makesrc - development version
#

INFO:
-----

	man page can be read by running:
		$ man ./makesrc.1.gz

INDEX:
------

		- 'makesrc' is the executable used for testing
		- 'build.sh' will "compile" all neccessary files into one executable "script"
		- 'makesrc.1.md' raw man page
